title: 1812-A
statement: A. Are You a Robot?time limit per test1 secondmemory limit per test256 megabytesinputstandard inputoutputstandard output

processed.result: You are given a string consisting of lowercase English letters. Determine if the string is a palindrome. A palindrome is a word, phrase, number, or other sequence of characters which reads the same backward as forward.
You are given a list of words. Determine if a given word is a robot-generated word based on its characteristics.
